249
00:17:40,029 --> 00:17:41,363
So.. - Both of them
are in the stomach.

250
00:17:41,446 --> 00:17:43,279
But no problem, no problem.

251
00:17:43,321 --> 00:17:45,529
Why, Grandpa?
Are they chocolate toffees..

252
00:17:45,613 --> 00:17:47,320
..that will melt away in the stomach?
- Tuktuk.

253
00:17:47,446 --> 00:17:48,821
No, dear, they won't melt.

254
00:17:49,113 --> 00:17:51,529
