Uncle, don't drag
my engagement into this.

1038
00:55:30,821 --> 00:55:34,488
You're already in this
and so is your engagement.

1039
00:55:35,738 --> 00:55:39,238
Raj, there's just one
way to stop his laughter.

1040
00:55:40,654 --> 00:55:42,488
No. No, I won't steal.

1041
00:55:42,571 --> 00:55:44,154
He won't steal..

1042
00:55:44,238 --> 00:55:45,988
Where are you going?

1043
00:55:46,071 --> 00:55:47,238
Stay here and talk to me.

1044
00:55:48,029 --> 00:55:50,571
Yash, I just swore on Sanjana inside..

1045
00:55:50,654 --> 00:55:52,321
