wrong again after today.

1046
00:55:52,779 --> 00:55:54,071
After today. - Yes.

1047
00:55:54,320 --> 00:55:56,488
This day won't end
until 12 o'clock midnight.

1048
00:55:56,904 --> 00:55:58,529
We'll finish the job by 11 o'clock.

1049
00:55:59,613 --> 00:56:00,696
Listen.

1050
00:56:00,988 --> 00:56:02,988
I have a foolproof plan..

1051
00:56:03,071 --> 00:56:04,613
