You go home and we'll get the money.

1054
00:56:13,488 --> 00:56:14,696
Home?

1055
00:56:15,779 --> 00:56:19,613
You don't know my home.
I don't know your home.

1056
00:56:20,279 --> 00:56:24,404
Uncle.. - Don't try to fool me.
Go fool someone else.

1057
00:56:28,279 --> 00:56:29,863
Until I get my money..

1058
00:56:29,946 --> 00:56:33,113
