you two like your shadow.

1059
00:56:33,696 --> 00:56:34,779
Understand.

1060
00:56:34,988 --> 00:56:38,154
Think that I am your boss now.

1061
00:56:38,571 --> 00:56:41,988
And you'll do as I say. Get that?

1062
00:56:43,363 --> 00:56:45,071
Okay, boss. - Okay.

1063
00:56:48,154 --> 00:56:49,320
See that.

1064
