tomorrow's breaking news.

1067
00:56:59,613 --> 00:57:00,821
How's that?

1068
00:57:01,696 --> 00:57:02,904
You'll be finished.

1069
00:57:04,696 --> 00:57:05,821
Funny.

1070
00:57:32,863 --> 00:57:34,154
Don't to go, Don't to go.

1071
00:57:34,238 --> 00:57:35,738
Take us out now. Quick.

1072
00:57:49,321 --> 00:57:52,738
Stop them! He's Marcos!

1073
00:59:00,321 --> 00:59:02,779
You said there are just two dogs.

1074
00:59:02,988 --> 00:59:04,321
Where did the third one come from?

1075
00:59:04,571 --> 00:59:06,738
The third one must be new. Come on.

1076
00:59:06,821 --> 00:59:10,238
We climbed up a 40-feet
wall and the gate is open.

1077
00:59:10,279 --> 00:59:12,363
Look. Is that the guard?

1078
00:59:12,863 --> 00:59:15,946
He's sleeping. - If he's sleeping,
go wake him up. Go.

1079
00:59:25,863 --> 00:59:27,529
Your saviours are dead.

1080
00:59:27,613 --> 00:59:28,738
Marcos.

1081
00:59:30,196 --> 00:59:31,363
Please.

1082
00:59:38,946 --> 00:59:40,071
Marcos.

1083
01:00:15,779 --> 01:00:17,946
The minister has a bank
right here in his house.

1084
