Yash, I suggest that
you take only what we need.

1085
01:00:20,863 --> 01:00:23,320
Here, go and count it.
- We won't count.

1086
01:00:23,529 --> 01:00:24,654
Did you count while robbing the bank?

1087
01:00:24,738 --> 01:00:27,029
I am the manager,
I know this was the amount. Take it.

1088
01:00:29,321 --> 01:00:30,488
Where are the diamonds?

1089
01:00:31,238 --> 01:00:32,779
Upstairs, in the safe.

1090
01:00:33,029 --> 01:00:34,154
Give it.

1091
01:00:34,529 --> 01:00:35,654
Give it. - Look, boss.

1092
01:00:35,863 --> 01:00:37,488
You'll have to take
the evening flight..

1093
