"Where is uncle?"

1096
01:00:42,946 --> 01:00:45,113
Then I'll have to attend
your wedding as well.

1097
01:00:45,613 --> 01:00:47,488
There's time for the wedding.

1098
01:00:47,779 --> 01:00:49,279
We'll say that uncle is dead.

1099
