Marcos, there's been
a robbery. - What?

1104
01:01:10,321 --> 01:01:12,238
Marcos, there's been a robbery.

1105
01:01:12,320 --> 01:01:14,320
Someone took my money
along with the diamonds?

1106
01:01:15,946 --> 01:01:18,238
I know you'll make excuses.

1107
01:01:18,613 --> 01:01:21,863
I've committed mass
bloodshed for these diamonds.

1108
01:01:22,071 --> 01:01:24,320
And now you say, "Marcos,
my belongings have been stolen.."

1109
01:01:24,363 --> 01:01:25,738
"..along with the diamonds."

1110
01:01:25,821 --> 01:01:27,988
Do we.. look like idiots?

1111
01:01:28,238 --> 01:01:31,113
I want my diamonds.

1112
01:01:31,279 --> 01:01:32,404
I want my diamonds. - Marcos.

1113
01:01:32,571 --> 01:01:34,613
I want my diamonds.

1114
01:01:34,946 --> 01:01:37,363
I want it!

1115
01:01:37,488 --> 01:01:39,363
