1116
01:01:39,488 --> 01:01:41,904
Marcos, stop.
What are you doing? - I want it.

1117
01:01:41,988 --> 01:01:43,279
He'll die. - I want it.

1118
01:01:43,321 --> 01:01:44,779
If he dies, we won't get the diamonds.

1119
01:01:45,320 --> 01:01:46,904
We won't get the diamonds.

1120
01:01:47,821 --> 01:01:51,071
Sorry. Sorry. Sorry, old man.

1121
01:01:52,279 --> 01:01:55,529
Sorry. DC. Give him a jolt.

1122
01:01:56,113 --> 01:01:58,571
Come here, Minister. - No.

1123
01:02:06,488 --> 01:02:07,654
Get up.

1124
01:02:10,488 --> 01:02:12,404
Boss, he's dead.

1125
01:02:13,488 --> 01:02:15,779
He's dead. Boss..

1126
01:02:18,363 --> 01:02:21,629
Boss, you told me so.

1127
01:02:21,738 --> 01:02:23,154
I told you to give him a jolt..

1128
01:02:23,238 --> 01:02:24,821
..I could've killed him too, fool.

1129
01:02:26,571 --> 01:02:28,529
Boss. Boss.

1130
01:02:30,529 --> 01:02:32,613
You can't die.

1131
01:02:33,904 --> 01:02:37,196
We're ruined.

1132
01:02:38,029 --> 01:02:39,320
It was a mistake, boss.

1133
