There's so much to do and..
he's lying here.

1139
01:02:55,488 --> 01:02:57,029
Tell me,
did you find the murder weapon..

1140
01:02:57,363 --> 01:02:59,238
The wire they used to electrocute him?

1141
01:02:59,320 --> 01:03:01,988
No, sir. The murderer
didn't leave behind any clue.

1142
01:03:02,404 --> 01:03:05,613
Naidu. Criminals first
leave evidence behind..

1143
01:03:05,696 --> 01:03:07,196
