1144
01:03:07,279 --> 01:03:09,488
You only need the eyes to see it.

1145
01:03:09,529 --> 01:03:10,654
Sir.

1146
01:03:11,821 --> 01:03:12,696
Sir.

1147
01:03:17,029 --> 01:03:18,196
Sir. Sir.

1148
01:03:18,404 --> 01:03:19,613
What, sir?

1149
01:03:20,196 --> 01:03:21,696
