2086
01:54:08,384 --> 01:54:09,343
Where is Sofia?

2087
01:54:10,718 --> 01:54:11,968
Where is Sophie?

2088
01:54:14,301 --> 01:54:16,843
Boss, that tall guy took Sophie.

2089
01:54:17,301 --> 01:54:20,134
