But he came to free his papa.

2090
01:54:20,634 --> 01:54:22,218
Instead he took the girl away.

2091
01:54:22,384 --> 01:54:25,468
See, he deceived us
as well and not just you.

2092
01:54:28,926 --> 01:54:31,051
Press it.
What are you staring at me for?

2093
01:54:31,176 --> 01:54:33,426
Keep pressing it till
they don't give us the address.

2094
01:54:34,134 --> 01:54:35,134
Keep pressing it.

2095
01:54:39,551 --> 01:54:41,051
Hello. - Do you want
the girl or the diamonds?

2096
01:54:41,134 --> 01:54:45,800
Hey. I thought you came here
to return the rest of the diamonds..

2097
01:54:45,843 --> 01:54:47,468
..and free your friends.

2098
01:54:47,493 --> 01:54:49,576
I didn't come there
to give the diamonds..

2099
01:54:50,093 --> 01:54:51,926
..but to take the
rest of the diamonds.

2100
01:54:52,468 --> 01:54:54,343
That's why I abducted your girl.

2101
01:54:54,384 --> 01:54:56,134
Where is Sophie? - What did you say?

2102
01:54:56,968 --> 01:54:59,551
It won't make any difference
to you even if I kill Sophia.

2103
01:54:59,926 --> 01:55:01,468
You just need the diamonds.

2104
01:55:01,718 --> 01:55:03,218
What are you saying..
- Marcos, you rascal.

2105
01:55:03,301 --> 01:55:05,551
You want to kill me.
- Cool down, baby. - I will kill you.

2106
01:55:05,634 --> 01:55:07,718
I will kill you.
- Take care of her. Sophie....

2107
01:55:07,926 --> 01:55:09,551
