2109
01:55:12,468 --> 01:55:14,843
Come with my men and the
diamonds to the 'Dhaba' (Inn).

2110
01:55:15,051 --> 01:55:18,043
The deal will be made there.
If you try to act smart..

2111
01:55:19,134 --> 01:55:21,800
