'Lassi' what is 'wassi'?

2193
02:01:19,051 --> 02:01:22,800
'Mutton-shatton', 'Murga-surga',
'Chai-shai', Parathe-sharathe'.

2194
02:01:23,218 --> 02:01:24,968
