Death couldn't kill me himself.

2199
02:01:34,634 --> 02:01:36,301
But this time I've made
foolproof arrangements.

2200
02:01:36,634 --> 02:01:40,051
I will surely die,
but all of you will die with me.

2201
02:01:40,218 --> 02:01:42,551
Death is very closeby. - Closeby?

2202
02:01:44,634 --> 02:01:47,718
What are you looking around for?
It's coming from above.

2203
02:01:47,800 --> 02:01:49,634
I have unscrewed all
the bolts of the ceiling.

2204
02:02:07,468 --> 02:02:11,301
Go. Go to heaven. Help us.

2205
02:02:14,718 --> 02:02:17,634
Hold it tight. Or else we'll die.

2206
02:02:20,301 --> 02:02:22,134
You all warded off death again.

2207
02:02:22,301 --> 02:02:25,384
