to do it for long. - Quiet.

2208
02:02:25,468 --> 02:02:28,051
You always try to die wherever we are.

2209
02:02:28,218 --> 02:02:29,800
How will I go to my village now?

2210
02:02:30,534 --> 02:02:32,468
Papa. - If I die..

2211
02:02:32,551 --> 02:02:34,134
Don't say that, Papa.

2212
02:02:35,718 --> 02:02:37,468
Your son is still alive.

2213
02:02:37,718 --> 02:02:39,800
Son. Why you..

2214
02:02:39,843 --> 02:02:41,468
I don't mean anything.

2215
02:02:41,926 --> 02:02:45,468
Did you come to save your
papa or to abduct the girl?

2216
02:02:45,551 --> 02:02:46,800
If I hadn't done that..

2217
02:02:46,843 --> 02:02:48,800
