killed our entire family.

2218
02:02:48,843 --> 02:02:51,134
What family? - You're my papa.

2219
02:02:51,551 --> 02:02:53,301
He isn't my friend
but my younger brother.

2220
02:02:53,384 --> 02:02:55,134
Your brother is dead.

2221
02:02:55,384 --> 02:02:56,968
For the sake of the diamonds..

2222
02:02:57,134 --> 02:02:58,218
..you told them to kill us.

2223
02:02:58,301 --> 02:02:59,800
Keep your diamonds with you.

2224
02:03:00,218 --> 02:03:03,551
No, Raj. Brother-in-law
didn't say that. - She is right.

2225
02:03:03,634 --> 02:03:06,634
