2236
02:03:28,468 --> 02:03:30,718
Boss, don't let him
check your back-pocket.

2237
02:03:30,800 --> 02:03:32,926
Hey, shut up!
- Thank you. One minute. - Hey!

2238
02:03:35,718 --> 02:03:37,718
Money is an evil thing.

2239
02:03:40,384 --> 02:03:42,800
